tensorflow/core/kernels/hexagon/hexagon_graph_execution_test.cc:70: Failure
Expected: (version) >= (1), actual: 0 vs 1
This line indicates that TF can't call a binary for hexagon. So, please answer following debugging questions.

  • What kind of Android device do you have? Basically, your Android device should have a special configuration to bypass qualcomm signature check. This functionality can't be enabled by software but you should use some specific hardwares like a dragon board.

  • What adb says? Please attach the output from "adb logcat".
